      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Combining a refined road presence with proven mechanical reliability, it offers a sophisticated and dependable driving experience. The interior and exterior reflect a history of attentive care, ensuring that this motorcar meets our rigorous standards for quality and performance. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, it stands as a testament to balanced value and enduring engineering.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
